        public Request getRequest(java.lang.String stringified)
        Description copied from interface: AppRequestParser
        An application must support string-to-Request conversion and back. Furthermore, the conversion to a string and back must preserve the return values of all InterfaceRequest methods, i.e., Application .getRequest(request.toString())).equals(request) must be true.
